e. Now your subordinates aren\u2019t just some resource; they are living people with their own strengths, weaknesses, fears and prejudices, and you'll have to reckon with all these things in order to survive.", "summary": "Interpret the law as you see fit in This Is the Police 2, sequel to the acclaimed noir drama This Is the Police! Run the sheriff's department, manage your cops, investigate, interrogate, and incarcerate. Make tough decisions - and try to keep out of prison yourself \u2013 in this story-driven mixture of adventure, strategy, and turn-based tactical combat.\nIs it a simulation? A management game? A tactical challenge? A visual novel? A puzzle? It's all of these, and more!", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 20, "name": "Thriller"}, {"id": 31, "name": "Drama"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/this-is-the-police-2", "videos": [{"id": 21328, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "huFqKqOvEp0", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=huFqKqOvEp0", "title": "This Is the Police 2 - 'Welcome to Sharpwood' Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/huFqKqOvEp0/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 18049, "name": "Announcement Trailer: Cold Blooded Attitude", "video_id": "sp9qtKUM-UQ", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sp9qtKUM-UQ", "title": "This Is The Police 2 - Announcement Trailer: Cold Blooded Attitude (4K)", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/sp9qtKUM-UQ/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 29237, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "GU5P35qbOMk", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GU5P35qbOMk", "title": "This Is the Police 2 - Mobile // Official Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/GU5P35qbOMk/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 21440, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "f9exnCXfx1w", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=f9exnCXfx1w", "title": "This Is the Police 2 - Release Trailer 'Why Am I Here' 4K", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/f9exnCXfx1w/maxresdefault.jpg"}, {"id": 19013, "name": "First Gameplay Trailer", "video_id": "RfIZhFWb34E", "url": "https://